  <source>Attikon Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the efficacy of the hydrolocalization technique for
      placement of popliteal perineural catheters in comparison with the stimulating catheters. A
      non inferiority trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
